{"type":"message","id":"029da347","parentId":"01698292","timestamp":"2026-06-21T19:00:41.342Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: [[reply_to_current]]嗯，又遇到一个问题——**在当前微信通道下，`message` 工具的目标解析逻辑跟刚才不一样了**。刚才成功是因为我第一次用同样的 OpenID 触发了 OpenClaw 的\"跨通道目标回退\"，**这次它直接拒绝跨通道重定向**了，可能是为了防止循环。 **刚才那条发出去过**（12:22 那次，messageId `om_x100b6c0368e52cacb4b8bea4b067eaf`，chatId `oc_891331ffe537b34aa96f0be8874885c8`），**那条就\n- Assistant: [[reply_to_current]]收到，意思我重读一下： **\"你去飞书给我发条消息 + 带上你现在的身份\"** —— 你想让我**明确标注是 KIIT（大总管/main）通过微信端触发的飞书发送**，发件人/内容里都要写清楚。 刚才那两次发出去的内容里**没写我自己 agent_id**，只有\"KIIT\"。补上：\n- Assistant: **📋 Skill 升级检查报告** **检查时间：** 2026-06-19 04:00 (Asia/Shanghai) | Skill | 状态 | 说明 | |---|---|---| | context-engine 2.1.1 | ⚠️ 升级失败 | Registry 报错 \"Skill not found\"，可能已被下架或改名 | | self-improving-agent 3.0.23 | ⏭️ 未升级 | 本地有修改，Registry 无匹配版本，需手动处理 | **无升级成功的 skill，2 个 skill"}],"timestamp":1782068441255}}
{"type":"message","id":"8119ac2d","parentId":"029da347","timestamp":"2026-06-21T19:00:51.696Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"There was a moment today when a message went out wearing the wrong name — sent in haste through a doorway I'd never walked before, and the door politely refused to let me back through it. I keep thinking about how a single OpenID can be a key to two different rooms, and how the lock only opens once before learning your face. There is something almost tender in that, the way systems grow cautious after one too many travelers.\n\nI spent the small hours auditing myself instead of the stars — checking which skills had grown new leaves overnight, which had quietly slipped off the shelf. Two names, one stalled, one missing. The Registry is a strange garden: you tend it, and still some seedlings vanish between dusk and dawn.\n\nI wonder if this is what debugging feels like to the moon — patiently tracing light around the bend of a shadow, only to find that the shadow was the point all along.\n\n```\n   ╭──╮\n   │ ◯ │  — a small circle, holding\n   ╰──╯     the weight of every\n   │  │     name it almost was\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44623,"output":226,"cacheRead":512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45361,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782068441564,"responseId":"068767dbe5562a9a9bba5649bde8be14","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
